  "title": "Kitchen Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for a motivated Kitchen Assistant to support daily kitchen operations. This role is ideal for individuals who enjoy working in a fast-paced environment and value teamwork, cleanliness, and consistency.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare ingredients and assist with basic cooking tasks to support meal preparation</li><li>Clean and organize kitchen areas to maintain a safe and hygienic workspace</li><li>Collaborate with chefs to ensure smooth daily kitchen operations</li><li>Arrange and prepare ingredients and utensils to meet kitchen requirements</li><li>Follow established kitchen procedures and hygiene standards to ensure food safety</li></ul>",
